---
title: Sriracha-Sesame Veg Gyozas and Prawn Noodles with Stir-Fried Veg and Sesame Seeds
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, our Sriracha-Sesame Veg Gyozas and Prawn Noodles bakes the gyozas to turn them crispy and golden on the outside. Spicy sriracha, ketjap manis, soy sauce and honey make a delicious sauce to coat the noodles.
